app_description: 100 Languages! Easily translate text photos or speech in over 100 languages Get Translation Wizard now! Word Bridge Translation Magic can easily translate any word phrase or sentence into multiple languages by clicking the corresponding translate button. We not only support text translation but also photo translation and voice translation to meet your translation needs in real time. Main features: Supports translation into more than 100 languages AI translation Real time speech reognition Real time photo recognition Translation result pronunciation Copy translation results Personalization: Translation usage history Privacy Policy: https: kyerbhcn.teradmadfus.com privacyPolicy.html Terms of Service: https: kyerbhcn.teradmadfus.com termsOfService.html
